data.description: If you are looking for a home in absolutely move in condition, this is the one for you! This stunning bungalow home was fully and tastefully renovated in 2019. The interior features an open floor plan with beautiful hardwood floors (that were refinished in 2020) and plenty of windows to let in all the natural light. The custom designed gourmet kitchen has newer stainless steel appliances, white shaker cabinets and Quartz countertops. The bathroom features a designer vanity and shiplap wood paneling. A screened front porch offers additional living space and is ideal for outdoor entertaining! The home has a huge backyard with ample room for a pool. No flood insurance is required! Excellent location! Just minutes away from downtown St Petersburg with its fine restaurants, breweries, outdoor cafes, shopping and museums. The white sand and blue water of the Gulf Beaches, Trader Joe's and Fresh Market is just a short car ride away. Come and see this magnificent home today and make it yours tomorrow before someone else does! While all information is believed to be accurate, Buyers are encouraged to confirm any information they deem necessary in making their decision to purchase.
